OL,3,CTwo men charged with murder after man
OL,4,Cstabbed in Whitstable
OL,6,FTwo men have been charged with murder
OL,7,Fafter a man was stabbed in Whitstable.
OL,9,FKent Police officers were called to a
OL,10,Freport a man had been assaulted in
OL,11,FBelmont Road at 2.04am on Friday 3
OL,12,FApril 2026.
OL,14,FOfficers went to the scene along with
OL,15,Fthe South East Coast Ambulance
OL,16,FService, where 19-year-old Ashton
OL,17,FHarrington was found to have suffered
OL,18,Finjuries consistent with stab wounds.
OL,19,FHe died at the scene.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
