OL,3,CTwo men charged with murder after man
OL,4,Cstabbed in Whitstable
OL,6,FOn Monday 13 April, two men were
OL,7,Farrested at a property in
OL,8,FSittingbourne.
OL,10,FThe Crown Prosecution Service has
OL,11,Fsince authorised a charge of murder
OL,12,Fagainst 19-year-old Kieron Barnes, of
OL,13,FRomney Court, Sittingbourne and 21-
OL,14,Fyear-old Tobias Agbaje, of Claremont
OL,15,FStreet, Herne Bay.
OL,17,FBoth men have also been charged with
OL,18,Fpossession of a bladed article.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/3
